            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Textverständnis Merlin (REA 42, 1940, 492): Invidia invidiosa, invicta d(e)a, s\{i\}aturab(er)is, q(u)is ne non tu(u)m c[o]llum f(r)egerit! Ist[ud] fia[t]!</p>
